  <description type="morphology">Plants 5–10(–18) dm. Flowering stems not fistulose, 2–5(–8) dm, tomentose to floccose. Leaves basal; blade 2–4 × 1.5–2 cm, tomentose abaxially, thinly floccose adaxially, margins plane. Inflorescences cymose, 20–50(–100) × 10–50 cm; branches tomentose to floccose. Involucres 3–6 per cluster, 3–5 mm, tomentose. Flowers 3–4 mm; perianth white to rose or yellow, pubescent. 2n = 40.</description>
